overview: The user wanted to enhance the visual appeal of their sleep
  questionnaire app, which they felt was functional but lacked aesthetic
  refinement. The agent initiated a comprehensive review of the app's styling,
  including global CSS, layout, and individual UI components. Based on this
  analysis, the agent identified several areas for improvement, such as the
  generic color palette, plain backgrounds, and basic form elements. The
  approach involved implementing a new, calming sleep-themed color palette,
  redesigning the main questionnaire form with improved progress indication and
  card styling, and enhancing the introductory section for a more welcoming
  experience. Furthermore, individual form fields like checkboxes and sliders
  were polished, and section groupings were refined to create a more cohesive
  and visually appealing interface. The outcome is a more sophisticated and
  user-friendly design that better aligns with the app's purpose of sleep
  assessment.
